ny pallies who were left behind port up.  They'd then die and get SC'ed and rezzed, while the wizard goes to the quest room and triggers Inte.  Then the pallies go to Inte one at a time and get their FA's and equip them, so the next one in line knows it's his turn (I think all the pallies who are waiting are guys atm).  Depending on time, etc. maybe we could continue on and hook up other players for their epic pieces, or head to Fear and get someone's FD.  What do you all think?    <p><center><imgsrc="http://www.prism.gatech.edu/~gte769i/images/balesig.gif"></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubalearic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balearic</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/5/02 9:02:26 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukalamad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kalamad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/5/02 11:34:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=322.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Proposal for the FA</span><hr size=1> Sounds great! Set a date <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><br>-------------------------<br>Kalamad Wolfrunner<br>54th season Paladin<br>Arma Aquetatis</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usirarris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sir Arris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Knight of Truth</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/5/02 2:58:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=322.topic&index=2>Reply</