romWeb?topicID=322.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Proposal for the FA</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub20.ezboard.com/fbloodsongfrm6.showMessage?topicID=334.topic">pub20.ezboard.com/fbloods...=334.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>No date set yet, but the time could be an issue.  Haladrim and Kalamad both live in Europe, and I think Faltan lives on the West Coast.  Most likely it'll be a Friday night or Sunday afternoon, my guess is sometime in the next couple weeks.  (Next Saturday is out because of a guild raid in the morning and another raid in the afternoon.)  I just want to see the screenshot on the Lanys boards of all five of us standing there on Pegasus Isle with our FA's!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>If anyone has a preference as far as date or time, please post it here.<br><br>Bale <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubalearic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balearic</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/5/02 8:29:10 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uleolan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leolan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><FONT COLOR=AA0000><B>Lanys.com Administrator</B></FONT></span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/6/02 1:24:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=322.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <b