hough, it can be hard to get the levels and gear needed to pull this off unless you have some good connections.<br><br>The route you take is entirely dependant on the assests you have available. Though remember, you're only going to 5th isle. Those raids you see requiring lvl 55+ people are the 3 day type deals that go much further into the plane and deal with MUCH more difficult mobs. Don't lose any sleep if you can't get a 60 shaman/enchanter, you don't NEED it. 55 would be a good number to set for a 5th isle raid for those 2 classes, you're not going to be staring down the Hand of Veeshan here.<br><br>Those are your two basic options from my experience. <p><center><hr width=450> <font face="Engravers MT"><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=12503 target=_blank>Arris Trueheart</a></font><BR>52nd <a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/pon target=_blank>Cavalier</a> of Mithanniel Marr<br>Of the <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/beqasylum target=_blank>Lanys T'Vyl</a> Server<br>Officer of <a href=http://www.eternalsinn.net target=_blank>Eternal Sinn</a><br><hr width=450></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usirarris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sir Arris</A> at: 1/8/02 6:04:39 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukalamad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kalamad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/8/02 2:31:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=322.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Proposal for the FA</span><hr size=1> Thanks Arris for the correction with the keys <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Personally I would 